      "work_around": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "A mitigation can be applied to the sssd.conf file that would make the occurrence of the race condition more difficult:\n\n1. Increase the GPO cache time out editing the following configuration directive in sssd.conf file:\n    a) ad_gpo_cache_timeout = 3600\n    Ps.: This value (3600) should make the cache time out in one hour but would make GPO updates propagation from AD server to local machines take longer.\n\n[1] https://access.redhat.com/documentation/pt-br/red_hat_enterprise_linux/7/html/windows_integration_guide/sssd-gpo"
        }
      ]
    },
    "nvd.nist.gov": {
